'''岩鬣蜥'''是[[岩鬣蜥屬|岩鬣蜥屬]]（''Cyclura''，又名圓尾蜥屬或圓尾鬣蜥屬）的[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]，分佈在[[加勒比地區|加勒比地區]]。<ref name="Dayhuff">{{Cite journal en|last=Dayhuff|first=Becky|title=Rock Iguanas of the Caribbean|journal=All at Sea Magazine|date=2006-02-01|url=http://www.allatsea.net/specificissueeditorial.php?featureid=660|access-date=2009-08-24|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407012732/http://www.allatsea.net/specificissueeditorial.php?featureid=660|dead-url=yes}}</ref>牠們是高度的[[特有種|特有種]]，在每一個島上都只有一個[[物種|物種]]或[[亞種|亞種]]。<ref name="Malone">{{cite book en|last=Malone|first=Catherine|last2=Davis|first2=Scott|chapter=Genetic Contributions to Caribbean Iguana Conservation|title= Iguanas: Biology and Conservation|publisher=University of California Press|pages=45–57|year=2004|isbn=9780520238541}}</ref><ref name="herp">{{cite journal en|last=Blair |first=David |title=West Indian Iguanas of The Genus ''Cyclura'' Their Current Status in the Wild, Conservation Priorities and Efforts to Breed Them in Captivity |journal=Northern California Herpetological Society Special Publication |volume=SE |number=6 |pages=55–56 |year=1991 |url=http://images.cyclura.com/download/pdf/WestIndianRockIguanas.PDF |format=PDF |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411062032/http://images.cyclura.com/download/pdf/WestIndianRockIguanas.PDF |archivedate=2008-04-11 }}</ref>

